Author: mourning-gory
Text: For some reason I got this too recently. Like, nothing seems appealing and it's just a waste of time. Pretty much apathy on my part, which like, has never happened before.

Author: Dalos_
Text: I personally can’t stand it. Eating is a painful chore that makes me feel horrible during and after. I lost the ability to enjoy good foods, which actually kind of sucks when I’m in a recovery mindset.
